\begin_inset Formula $C_{div}$
\end_inset

 liberated by the A/D converter, the voltage divider output voltage is
\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
V_{div}=\frac{C_{div}}{1023}V_{ref}
