\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Aside from the diode drop of the peak detector, the parasitic power draw
 of the PIC18, and load resistance error discussed previously, several other
 factors contribute to error in the power reading.
 These include absolute error of the A/D converter, voltage reference drift,
 and error in the voltage divider resistances.
\end_layout

